### ============================================================================
### FAMILY TRIPS — /api/v1/family-trips + /api/v1/family-package-purchases
### ============================================================================

### ─── Family Trips ──────────────────────────────────────────

### Get my family trips
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/family-trips
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Preview family trip
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/family-trips/preview
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "packageType": "FAMILY_5",
  "destination": "London, UK",
  "country": "United Kingdom",
  "duration": 10,
  "purpose": "Family vacation",
  "tripType": "LEISURE",
  "members": [
    {"firstName": "John", "lastName": "Doe", "relationship": "SELF"},
    {"firstName": "Jane", "lastName": "Doe", "relationship": "SPOUSE"},
    {"firstName": "Jimmy", "lastName": "Doe", "relationship": "CHILD"}
  ]
}

### Save family trip draft
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/family-trips/drafts
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "packageType": "FAMILY_3",
  "destination": "Paris, France",
  "country": "France",
  "duration": 7,
  "purpose": "Family vacation",
  "tripType": "LEISURE",
  "members": [
    {"firstName": "John", "lastName": "Doe", "relationship": "SELF"},
    {"firstName": "Jane", "lastName": "Doe", "relationship": "SPOUSE"}
  ]
}

### Get latest draft
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/family-trips/drafts/latest
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get family trip by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/family-trips/{{familyTripId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Update family trip
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/family-trips/{{familyTripId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "packageType": "FAMILY_5",
  "destination": "Paris, France",
  "country": "France",
  "duration": 10,
  "purpose": "Extended family vacation",
  "tripType": "LEISURE",
  "members": [
    {"firstName": "John", "lastName": "Doe", "relationship": "SELF"},
    {"firstName": "Jane", "lastName": "Doe", "relationship": "SPOUSE"},
    {"firstName": "Jimmy", "lastName": "Doe", "relationship": "CHILD"}
  ]
}

### Submit family trip
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/family-trips/{{familyTripId}}/submit
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Delete family trip
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/family-trips/{{familyTripId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get trip plans
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/family-trips/{{familyTripId}}/plans
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Regenerate member code
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/family-trips/{{familyTripId}}/members/{{familyMemberId}}/regenerate-code
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### ─── Family Members ────────────────────────────────────────

### Member login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/family-trips/members/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mainApplicantEmail": "john.doe@example.com",
  "code": "MEMBER-LOGIN-CODE-123"
}

### Member logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/family-trips/members/logout
X-Family-Member-Token: <family-member-token>

### Get current member info
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/family-trips/members/me
X-Family-Member-Token: <family-member-token>

### Get member plans
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/family-trips/members/plans
X-Family-Member-Token: <family-member-token>

### Get member plan detail
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/family-trips/members/plans/{{planId}}
X-Family-Member-Token: <family-member-token>

### ─── Family Package Purchases ──────────────────────────────

### Checkout family package
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/family-package-purchases/checkout
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "packageType": "FAMILY_5",
  "currency": "USD",
  "additionalMembers": 0,
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "phone": "+2348012345678"
}

### Family package payment callback
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/family-package-purchases/callback?tx_ref={{txRef}}&status=successful

### Get active purchases
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/family-package-purchases/active
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Purchase history
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/family-package-purchases/history
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
